{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01FrKssUtuiD7QciFwA3JFuY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The application is a Spring Boot + JSF (JoinFaces) Address Book with:\n- JPA entity (`Contact`), Spring Data JPA repository, Service layer, JSF controller\n- H2 in-memory database\n- XHTML/JSF frontend pages\n\n**Migration strategy:** Since Quarkus doesn't support JSF/JoinFaces, I'll convert the JSF frontend to a REST API with equivalent CRUD functionality, keeping the same entity, and providing a simple HTML frontend. The business logic and data model remain identical.\n\nLet me now create all the migrated files:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":454,"cache_read_input_tokens":42159,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":454,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":521},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d72ec4a1-bfc7-4aa5-bf05-2da291fff045","uuid":"6422d5b4-f7a0-4f63-bacc-88582ef966ee"}
